<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <p xml:id="Aink229-kilavi">varaiviṭai vaittup pirinta talaimakaṉ mīṇṭāṉ eṉpatu kēṭṭut talaimakaṭk eytiya kaviṉait tōḻi tāṉ aṟiyātāṇ pōṉṟ avaḷai viṉāviyatu </p>
      <p xml:lang="en"> The confidante, questioning the heroine as though unaware, about the beauty that has come to her, having heard that the hero—who placed a gap in the marriage and departed—has returned.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink229">
<l>amma vāḻi tōḻi nāmaḻap</l>
<l>paṉṉāḷ pirinta vaṟaṉi lāḷaṉ</l>
<l>vantaṉa ṉōmaṟ ṟiraviṟ</l>
<l>poṉpōl viṟaṟkaviṉ koḷḷuniṉ ṉutalē</l>
</lg>
<lg xml:lang="en">
  <l>  O friend, — </l>
  <l rend="space">did that duty-less man,  </l>
  <l>who parted [from us] for many days, as we weep,  </l>
  <l>come subsequently at night?    </l>
  <l rend="space indent">Your forehead takes on a triumphant beauty, like gold.  </l>
</lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
